Field Detail

TIMEOUT_NEVER

public static final int TIMEOUT_NEVER
Timeout to use in AjaxOptions.cacheTimeout(long) in order to specify that the cached response will only be timed out when clearCache() is called or, if maxSize is greater than 0, if the size is too large, and this has not been accessed recently.

See Also:
Constant Field Values

TIMEOUT_NEVER_CLEAR_FROM_CACHE

public static final int TIMEOUT_NEVER_CLEAR_FROM_CACHE
Timeout to use in AjaxOptions.cacheTimeout(long) in order to specify that the cached response will never be cleared unless removeEntry(AjaxOptions) or removeEntry(String) is specifically called. Additionally, maxSize and LRU algorithms will not affect these entries.

See Also:
